- Open browser
- Login to Admin Panel (localhost/abc/wp-admin)
- Pages --> All Pages
	- select page --> click on "Edit" button
		Text: copy text and peste here
		Image: click on "+" button --> Image
			- click on "Upload" button and select image
			- to set "Thumbnail Image" --> click on "Documents" --> Featured Image
			           --> Upload Files --> select image
		Gellery: click on "+" button --> Gellery
			- click on "Upload" button and select multiple image
			- gelery settings:
				Columns: 4

- click on "Publish" button to save


 
			
